---
title: Savoury Mushroom Tacos with Creamy Kale Slaw
description: Everything tastes better in taco form. Case in point: this marvellous mash-up! Steamy tortillas are filled with crispy creminis and topped with tender, creamy kale slaw. The best part? They’re ready in a jiffy, and couldn’t be easier to whip up. Taco night just got a whole lot better!
